{"tid":1792990,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"分左手之後確診抑鬱，點先可以move on到？","createTime":"2019-12-22T04:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T07:21:00.000Z","uid":209107,"like":7,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"5190081c8839dc83c8be20ec5114cef4bf86225e","tid":1792990,"uid":209107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"自從ex上左莊之後，我就不斷好焦慮。我每一晚都訓唔好，成日幻想到佢喺hall同人 玩到好埋。搞到佢覺得我完全唔信任佢。同埋我份人好小氣好計較，好好勝，好鍾意比較。所以我成日因為待遇唔同而話佢，搞到佢好難受。直到分手之後，我一開始以為係佢喺hall有曖昧對象,所以令佢下定決心分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但後來諗返自己有幾咁唔成熟。覺得自已好無用，連體諒同支持伴侶都唔識。<br />\n分左手兩個月，我每日都係喊住起身流住眼淚訓。對佢嘅愛並無隨住時間流逝而減淡。每日都自責自己唔成熟所以搞成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後老母覺得我好痴線，帶左我睇精神科醫生。之後確診左患上抑鬱。再加上自己本身有長期病，所以食藥食到個人好攰好辛苦。<br />\n好在最近pass左消防體能，覺得自己冇咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b311c75c39b252348c6abd3d3b33eda2d3790f82","tid":1792990,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-22T05:08:16.000Z","msg":"大隻絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc95a3a44738f0af4a907058cdf35fca7070a574","tid":1792990,"uid":209107,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b311c75c39b252348c6abd3d3b33eda2d3790f82","tid":1792990,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-